{"tid":2006542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只有大麻可以救香港","createTime":"2020-05-08T00:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T02:37:21.000Z","uid":65638,"like":27,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"18c183052e3f8a2fba7b48e931cc8f82c7ec1676","tid":2006542,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:12:28.000Z","msg":"中共再咁落去，美國會制裁香港，外資會慢慢走，香港經濟玩完，大家欖炒。但有無諗過欖炒之後點？ 假設最後港共收皮，經濟都係差左，外國投資者已經走得7788, 呢個時候就要靠大麻，開放醫療娛樂用合法化，嚴加限制年齡同使用大麻地區，香港就變成亞洲第一大麻港，科學園同數碼港可以研究新品種，工業區可以做水耕同大麻加工產品，基本上100%無得輸，到時香港誓必變亞洲第一"},{"pid":"efe83d6a48d81ba0a2ece833f7968d6f17e0e633","tid":2006542,"uid":85461,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"South Park 情節"},{"pid":"c4ac6c66fd4629b90412962b74a9af517857a65f","tid":2006542,"uid":37443,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:14:59.000Z","msg":"以前夠話開間賭場 <br />\n以香港既配套一定收澳門皮<br />\n不過因為大陸驚澳門冇飯開叫停左<br />\n而家所有野都係政治問題"},{"pid":"89417acd4a0ba1cc1f4c5bccabbafe853549677a","tid":2006542,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe83d6a48d81ba0a2ece833f7968d6f17e0e633","tid":2006542,"uid":85461,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"South Park 情節"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:15:23.000Z","msg":"現實係可行<br />\n你睇外國一d 地區果時岩岩開放<br />\n排哂長龍，仲有大麻股票都升到澎澎聲"},{"pid":"88ec2eee39fcb88febee4daf977b3c7f167f40c6","tid":2006542,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"d51945f143a08ca5da3e189024f3bc2b1678a9d2","tid":2006542,"uid":37912,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1acaecb78d80bfe39963762a7ca7bca42a2d7630","tid":2006542,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4ac6c66fd4629b90412962b74a9af517857a65f","tid":2006542,"uid":37443,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:14:59.000Z","msg":"以